com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata

Class FixFieldInfos

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata.FieldInfos
      • com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata.FixFieldInfos
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFieldInfos, IFixFieldInfos

    public class FixFieldInfos
extends FieldInfos
implements IFixFieldInfos
    Default market data IFieldInfos implementation.

    This provides the mapping between market data fields (via their IDs) and their counterparts in the FIX protocol.

    Normally this class would be part of the FIX market data project - however in the interests of not creating a dependency between this util market data project and the FIX market data project, it is defined here. At the end of the day, it just provides a mapping between field ID's and some ints and Strings. There is not really anything strongly FIX related in that, except that those int's and String's happen to be related to FIX MDEntryType and FIX tag values.

    In practice it is handy to have the default FieldInfos mapping relate to FIX - but without needing to introduce a project dependency.

    Author:
    John Cameron
